{"tid":1172113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺得邊間銀行嘅服務最差？","createTime":"2019-05-26T08:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T08:57:18.000Z","uid":31386,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"89fa2d872c341def46d6d8b8035515ac9216d426","tid":1172113,"uid":31386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T08:05:05.000Z","msg":"我用過五六間銀行 覺得東亞成個user experience真係差到冇人有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢個app係白癡到如果你同一時間有兩張東亞信用卡 想登入時就會係咁bug 用新嘅信用卡號碼同自訂嘅user name都唔會登入到 係咁彈error message話你個電話號碼已經link咗去另一個Account 要你用舊嘅信用卡號碼(16位)登入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒多幾次仲鎖埋你個account 叫你打個星期六日唔會有人聽嘅電話號碼去reset<br />\n<br />\n換迎新禮品有任何問題 亦都唔會主動通知你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係要你打幾十次電話 send晒email 先慢慢幫你跟下 搞足你大半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦 宜家想cut卡 仲難過cut有線 又要你換埋啲分 又要鎖咗你個網上銀行 真係俾佢折磨到身心俱疲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都係果句啦 明明銀行係應該幫手處理生活上嘅transactions 點解現實中成日都係調返轉頭 好似要你serve間bank咁 幫佢做呢樣果樣 嘥你勁多時間同佢溝通"},{"pid":"0ead1d0fea4ef951e733eb3d8d007140df7bbfa9","tid":1172113,"uid":174530,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T08:07:03.000Z","msg":"戶口得幾百蚊？<br />\n我戶口幾千萬cash，次次去都有女經理幫我含"},{"pid":"b1a848a943a179bfe76c0a0fee96fe809ce195ba","tid":1172113,"uid":31386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ead1d0fea4ef951e733eb3d8d007140df7bbfa9","tid":1172113,"uid":174530,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T08:07:03.000Z","msg":"戶口得幾百蚊？<br />\n我戶口幾千萬cash，次次去都有女經理幫我含"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T08:57:18.000Z","msg":"仲敢用佢savings咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 浄係得信用卡已經cut都cut唔切"}]}